Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: pi-top <deb-maintainers@pi-top.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7), dh-python, dh-systemd (>= 1.5)
Standards-Version: 3.8.4
Homepage: https://pi-top.com/

Package: pt-sys-oled
Architecture: armhf
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, fonts-freefont-ttf,
 pt-hub, pt-ui-mods, python3-luma-oled, python3-luma-core,
 python3-monotonic, python3-psutil, python3-pt-common,
 python3-pt-oled
Recommends: pt-remote-rpi
Description: pi-top OLED system menu application
 The intended behaviour of this application is to manage
 user projects and display important system information
 onto the onboard OLED screen. Navigation is managed
 by the onboard buttons, which is handled by the
 centralised pi-top device manager.
